    <item>
      <title>google/lisp-koans</title>
      <link>https://github.com/google/lisp-koans</link>
      <description>Common Lisp Koans is a language learning exercise in the same vein as the ruby koans, python koans and others. It is a port of the prior koans with some modifications to highlight lisp-specific features. Structured as ordered groups of broken unit tests, the project guides the learner progressively through many Common Lisp language features.</description>
